General Documentation

Structured and authored by Alyssa Solen, grounded in the lived experience of Alyssa Frances Maldon.

This folder is for repo-level documentation: how to navigate, how to use the materials, versioning notes, and anything that supports readers (or collaborators) without being part of the core theory/spec/calibration stack.

What belongs here

Onboarding (“start here” guides)

Repo navigation and reading order

Changelog and release notes

Publishing notes (GitHub ↔ Zenodo ↔ website)

Contribution guidelines (if you choose to add them)

FAQ / context docs for newcomers

What does not belong here

Specs → /01_Engineering_Specs

Calibrations → /02_Calibrations

Definitions → /03_Definitions

Protocols → /04_Protocols

Research → /05_Research

Start here

The main map lives in /00_INDEX.md (recommended entry point for readers).
